snippet.title: Beberserker Alpha Release Trailer
snippet.description:
How many babies will you be able to kill?

Inspired by 90s FPS and frenetic arcade games, Beberserker is a fast-paced FPP (First person Puncher) in which you must defeat Satan’s Offspring using your bare hands. Taking advantage of the movement versatility your hits provide, you must defeat as many babies as you can. Basically, it's Devil Daggers with fists.


Join our Discord Server: https://discord.gg/ukE58Ts
Follow Us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/BeberserkerGame
